"<em>Accu-menu</em> <media type=\"image\" mime=\"image/svg\" "
"src=\"/usr/share/icons/ubuntu-mono-light/status/24/battery-100.svg\">Accu-"
"pictogram</media>"

#: C/unity-appmenu-intro.page:32(item/p)
